                        <div class="mainHd">University Research</div>
                        <div class="textBox">
                            The gateway to studying at internationally recognized universities starts here; as the
                            University of
                            Science and Technology is the first university in Yemen to offer a group of international
                            programs
                            in various fields, which provide students with future prospects to gain knowledge and reach
                            an
                            internationally accredited degree.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            Four peer-reviewed scientific journals issued by the university, namely (Journal of Social
                            Studies,
                            International Journal for the Development of Excellence, Arab Journal for Quality Assurance
                            of
                            University Education, Journal of Science and Technology), obtained advanced positions out of
                            only 9
                            Yemeni scientific journals that met the accreditation criteria and were granted an impact
                            factor
                            for
                            the year 2020, and out of 434 peer-reviewed scientific journals at the Arab level.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            The impact factor is considered a measure of the importance of peer-reviewed scientific
                            journals
                            within the field of (IF) or (Impact Factor), and it reflects the extent to which new
                            research
                            refers
                            to and cites research previously published in that journal. It also expresses the citation
                            rate
                            to
                            the number of items published during the past two years of the journal, in addition to the
                            originality and scientific quality of the published research, the technical quality of the
                            editorial
                            board, the regularity of the journal's publication, in addition to the research arbitration
                            system
                            in it, and commitment to the ethics of scientific research and publication.
                        </div>
